name: Whillas & Gunn -  Small Trap Duffle in Rosemary
description:
"Our most trusted companion, the Trap Duffle from Whillas & Gunn is the everyday, anywhere bag that has been on every one of our adventures to date. Although it is timeless and simple, the signature webbing detail will set this carry all apart from the rest - and it fits in the overhead on a plane no sweat. The end pockets provides easy access to your passport and phone when on the move and the detachable strap allows you to carry it as a messenger – freeing your hands up for taking photos or eating a slice of pizza on the run." W&G

- Constructed from heavy-weight bonded “Drought Canvas”

- Antique copper hardware and cowhide trim

- Detachable & adjustable strap

- Signature webbing detail

- Tobacco striped cotton lining with inner security pockets

- L-42cm / W-24cm / H-31cm

name: Whillas & Gunn - Nullabor Tote Sage

-Leather tipped drawcord closure
- Inner security pocket
- Signature webbing

- L-44 cm / W-10cm / H-43cm

name: Moscot - Glick Grey
description:
Great Aunt Ruth used to always say, "You are the glick of my heart, " to indicate someone or something she loved. Odd? Perhaps…but, with attributes of The LEMTOSH, The MILTZEN, and The ZOLMAN all rolled into one, we’re pretty sure you’ll love The GLICK enough to make #YouAreTheGLICKofMyHeart not odd at all. Made from acetate with two adjoined dot rivets on the front and temples, a key hole bridge, and a real three barrel hinge.

Lenses: G15

name: Rains - Jacket Ltd
description:
The jacket has a regular casual fit. Button fastening in front, and two functional front pockets. The hood is adjustable, and has a practical cap. Under the back shield and under arm are air circulation holes to ensure comfort. This is the classic universal short rain jacket for everyday use.

50% PU (polyurethane), 50% Polyester.

name: Rains - Curve Jacket
description:
The jacket has a tapered fit, making an elegant and classic look. With waterproof zipper, button closing, two rectangular pockets, and adjustable belt in the waist. The Curve Jacket is a modern interpretation of the traditional trench coat. A feminine and classic look for the rainy days.

50% PU (polyurethane), 50% Polyester.

name: Jason Markk - Quick Wipes
description:
12 wipes per box. Quick Wipes come individually packaged making it convenient to have a couple on you at all times - whether you're headed to the club, school, or…anywhere! Each wipe is dual-textured for the ultimate in cleaning versatility on the go! One side of the wipe contains small blue dots which offers a slight abrasiveness and comes in handy when working out tougher stains - while the softer white side is great for general cleaning.

    Superior cleaning ability
    Extremely durable
    Unique dual-textured substrate (wipe material)

NOTE: This product is not to be used on suede and/or nubuck.

name: Jason Markk - 4 oz. Premium Kit
description:
Complete set. Includes 4 oz. Premium Shoe Cleaner and Standard Shoe Cleaning Brush packaged in resealable, Jason Markk fresh pouch.

    OR/ORIGINAL
    4 oz. Premium Sneaker Solution
    Does not contain any harsh chemicals or abrasives
    98.3% Natural and completely biodegradable
    Safe on all colors and materials
    Effectively cleans and conditions
    Cleans up to 100 pairs of sneakers

Standard Sneaker Cleaning Brush

    Synthetic bristle
    Handcrafted wood block brush
    Laser-etched Jason Markk logo on handle
    Excellent for tackling dirt on midsoles
    Great for all-around cleaning
    Tough on stubborn stains

NOTE: When cleaning premium leather, suede, nubuck, nylon, cotton mesh and other delicate materials take extra care and be gentle. We highly recommend using our Premium Shoe Cleaning Brush. The softer hog bristles are better suited for use on delicate surfaces. 

Here is a short video of how to use: http://vimeo.com/jasonmarkk/how-to

**SHIPPING FOR THIS PRODUCT ONLY AVAILABLE WITHIN AUSTRALIA.

name: Le Coq Sportif - Retro Running Crew Sweat

name: Antipodium - Instict Pullover in Celadon
description:
Texture blocking, careful attention to detail and a contemporary palette informed the design of the Instinct Pullover. Clashing textures of leather, velour and heavyweight brushed jersey in contrast hues take its cues from the classic sweatshirt. The result - an instinctually versatile, loose fitting and easy to wear piece.

- Made in brushed interlock, velour and nappa leather
- Relaxed fit, round neckline, set-in raglan sleeves, ribbed cuffs and hem
- Leather v-neck detail and elbow patches

name: Antipodium - Instict Pullover in Plum
description:
Texture blocking, careful attention to detail and a contemporary palette informed the design of the Instinct Pullover. Clashing textures of leather, velour and heavyweight brushed jersey in contrast scarlet hues take its cues from the classic sweatshirt. The result - an instinctually versatile, loose fitting and easy to wear piece.

name: Antipodium - Instict Bodice in Plum
description:
A clever piece for Autumn Winter, this sexy sleeveless bodice is crafted in nappa leather and can be layered with or without a prim rollneck for a subverted look. Featuring a slightly flared peplum and tantalising semi-sheer mesh back panel, the panelled shape curves on the body to accentuate a flattering silhouette.

- Made of nappa leather
- Flattering bodice, peplum detail, open-end zip with ribbon guard for comfort, mesh back panel, fully lined
- Panelled shape creates a flattering silhouette

description:
The thrill of the semi-sheer Surveillance Blouse is the combination of delicate black silk georgette and contrasting mustard suede collar and white grosgrain seam detailing. A versatile blouse that works with the Concorde Shorts and Slicker Skirt.
